title: Qiskit Fall Fest
desc1: Qiskit Fall Fest is a global hackathon series hosted annually by <blue>IBM Quantum</blue> to help university students around the world learn and experience quantum computing using Qiskit.
desc2: Each university independently plans and hosts its own Qiskit Fall Fest event, where participants explore a wide range of quantum computing topics and build projects. Students from any background are welcome to participate.
